This directory holds all auto-generated test outputs.
Do NOT commit to source control (add tests/outputs/ to .gitignore).

Generated files:
  benchmark_results.csv      — Phase 2 comparative metrics table
  benchmark_summary.txt      — Phase 2 human-readable summary
  aami_metrics_full.csv      — Phase 3 per-record AAMI detail
  aami_stats.txt             — Phase 3 Wilcoxon + Cohen's d results
  attention_maps/            — Phase 4 high-res PNG XAI figures
  ch8_tables.tex             — Phase 5 LaTeX thesis tables
  ch8_ablation.csv           — Phase 5 ablation study results
  ch8_draft.md               — Phase 5 Results & Discussion draft
